data.description: The Living is Easy Here! Skip the Endless Sitting in Traffic & Start Enjoying Life! Great Floorplan that is Very Adaptable. Hardwoods (Main Level), New Laminate Flooring (Downstairs), & Tile. New Paint, Double Paned Windows (with 2" Blinds), Roof & Soffits in Last 10 Years. Big Kitchen with Extra Cabinet & Counter Space, Tile Backsplash, Inset Lighting, Opens to Living Room & Deck - Feels Like Open Concept but Enough Walls to Hang Art & Divide the Space.  LR, Kitchen, Eating Area, 3 BR & BA Upstairs. Downstairs, You Find BR, BA, Den, Laundry, HUGE Closet (this was Used as an Office!), & Garage! Fenced Yard with Open & Covered Deck, Storage Building, Firepit, and an Extra Parking Space by the Garage. Home Warranty and with Acceptable Offer, Seller Provides a 2/1 Buy Down (with acceptable terms).
